      • removeObject

        public void removeObject​(greenfoot.Actor object)
        If an MPActor is removed, then broadcast a command to remove the actor from other clients. If this client is in a room, the message will be broadcast to the room, otherwise it will be broadcast to all other clients. Before an MPActor is removed, this method will call MPActor.willBeRemoved() and after an MPActor has been removed, this method will call MPActor.hasBeenRemoved(MPWorld), passing this world as the parameter.
